{
  "text": "For comparative analysis with the rice or Brachypodium genome, tentative consensus (TC) or EST sequences were subjected to BLASTn searches of the rice genomic sequences in the Gramene database [CITATION_1] ; http:// www.gramene.org/Multi/blastview) or to search of Brachypodium super contigs (http://www.brachypodium.org). For BLASTn searches, the threshold limits for signiWcant hits were at least 80% nucleotide identity for at least 60 bases. We set e-value <e \u00a17 in order to include maximum number of EST or TC hits with lowest e-value. When several signiWcant hits were found, only the best hit was adopted.",
  "citation_candidates": [
